duct linksHistoric news or related articles can link through to an existing Press Office article or other website to provide a holistic picture of your companyYou can feature and link related products, by name and shirt descriptor copyVisit the Biz Digitorial example, and enquire about one month’s exposure for your most current company or brand news within the heart of your business media space on Bizcommunity. Contact moc.ytinummoczib@selas today to discuss converting your press releases to digitorial on Biz!